	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I made a Famicom Hangman game. The program is complete (although new things might still be added, but I think it is complete), but not all phrases are complete. If you have any, you can please suggest new words/phrases to add on. Also tell me any other question/comment/complaints you have. Even modify the program if you want to; it is public domain. If someone want to make label for 60-pins cartridge, I may also include that in the ZIP archive as well.<br /><br />Wiki: <a href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Famicom_Hangman" class="postlink">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/Famicom_Hangman</a>

		

		</td>
